| File | Role |
|------|------|
| `common/chat.cpp` | **Only file to change** — add handler function + detection block |
| `common/chat-peg-parser.cpp` | Reference only: `standard_json_tools()` is defined here and available via `p.standard_json_tools(...)` in any `build_chat_peg_parser` lambda |
| `common/chat-peg-parser.h` | Reference only: `standard_json_tools` declared at line 108 |
| `models/templates/mistralai-Mistral-Nemo-Instruct-2407.jinja` | Reference only: the exact Jinja template this handler targets |

